HEADWORD: Training wheels
<hw>Train"ing wheels</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>a pair of small wheels
attached to the rear of a bicycle to keep the bicycle upright; -- used
to assist those, especially small children, learning how to ride a
bicycle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trainman</ent>⟦br⟧
